author: Christine Rousselle
title: Rioters Set Limousine Ablaze in Downtown D.C.
text:
Rioters Set Limousine Ablaze in Downtown D.C. Share 
Earlier today, anti-Trump protestors rioted, smashed some windows and spray-painted some graffiti. Now they've lit a limousine on fire. Someone set the limo on fire. pic.twitter.com/y4AFr5HNjk — Matt Pearce (@mattdpearce) January 20, 2017 Trump protestors have lit a limo on fire: #Inauguration : pic.twitter.com/vFfALkjHOz — Ellie Hall (@ellievhall) January 20, 2017 PHOTO: Anti-Trump protesters set a limo on fire amid #Inauguration festivities. #TRUMP45 (??: @sveinschwab ) pic.twitter.com/eV8qctanSr — Fox News (@FoxNews) January 20, 2017 
The fire grew quite large and was eventually extinguished. Here's my account of the limo fire I just saw. @FordFischer #DisruptJ20 #Inauguration pic.twitter.com/W9foYv85th — Alejandro Alvarez (@aletweetsnews) January 20, 2017 
What in the hell are these people thinking?
